yingyinNormal.en: That was San Diego Comic-Con. This is Bakersfield Comic-Con.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上次是圣地亚哥动漫大会，这次是贝克尔斯菲动漫大会。

yingyinNormal.en: Really? In a comic book store?
yingyinNormal.zh: 在漫画店里这样好吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I feel like you guys just went to Comic-Con.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们不是才去过动漫大会吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I missed Comic Con and the new Star Trek movie!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我错过了动漫展，连新的《星际迷航》电影也错过啦！

yingyinNormal.en: Amy has a fondness for the comic strip Marmaduke.
yingyinNormal.zh: Amy非常喜欢《大丹麦狗马默杜克》这部漫画。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm considering investing in Stuart's comic book store. Interesting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在考虑投资斯图尔特的漫画店。有意思。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you need anything from the shops? Maybe a newspaper, and comic Newspaper, comic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 需要帮你们从超市带点什么吗。也许我需要一份报纸吧，还有漫画。一份报纸，漫画。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. Let's go to the comic book store. We went to the comic book store last night.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好啊，我们去漫画书店吧。我们昨晚就去过了。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't want to take any shirt off at Comic-Con. If I may speak for Comic-Con, we don't want that either.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不想在漫展上脱掉上衣啊。如果我能代漫展发言，我会说我们也不希望这是发生。

yingyinNormal.en: That's how much buying a comic book store means to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为了买下漫画店，我豁出去了。

yingyinNormal.en: I've never even read a comic book. You guys? Uh-uh. No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没有看过漫画书呢，你们呢？没。没有过。

yingyinNormal.en: If you don't do this, I won't take you to the comic book store.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你再不出来，我就不带你去动漫书店。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm assuming these are some kind of horns they bought at Comic-Con?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我猜你说的"角"，是他们从动漫展买的什么号"角"之类吧？

yingyinNormal.en: What do we have here? An old comic. That was my favorite comic. A tin toy. My favorite toy. Music. My favorite record. And a very old carrot. That's mine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是一本旧的漫画书。那个是我最喜欢的漫画书！缎子的玩具。那是我最喜欢的玩具。一张唱片。是我最喜欢的唱片。还有一根很老很老的胡萝卜。这是我的。

yingyinNormal.en: Hi! Hey. Guess who's going to be at the comic bookstore on Thursday?
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨。嘿。猜猜看，周四谁会去漫画店？

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you, but it doesn't look like I'm going to Comic-Con this year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢，但看起来今年我是无缘漫展了。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you planning on sitting here? No, I'm going to the comic book store.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你准备坐这么？不，我要去漫画店。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know, Raj. Maybe the comic book store doesn't have a bulletin board.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我怎么知道，拉杰，没准是因为漫画书店没有布告栏。

yingyinNormal.en: Very well. Hey, Comic-Con tickets go on sale this Firday. You can't buy one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 非常好，漫展的票这周五开卖，你不许买。

yingyinNormal.en: Amy, the comic book store is like my version of the country in Black Panther.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾米，漫画书店对我来说就像《黑豹》里的那个国家。
